    "skill": "Transitions",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "passage": "\"Wishcycling\"—putting nonrecyclable items into recycling bins under the mistaken belief that those items can be recycled—\nultimately does more harm than good. Nonrecyclable items, such as greasy pizza boxes, can contaminate recyclable materials,\nrendering entire batches unusable. ______ nonrecyclable products can damage recycling plants' machinery.",
